    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
      Terms of
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 via-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Use</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      The rules of the road for using EversPass. We've kept them as simple and fair as possible.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Terms Content -->
